my whole body is racing,

282
00:18:25,764 --> 00:18:28,264
止まらない鼓動強く
my unstoppable heartbeat growing stronger.

283
00:18:28,264 --> 00:18:33,764
そう高く 果てなく
So high, endlessly,

284
00:18:33,764 --> 00:18:36,764
抱きしめた未来が
the future we embraced

285
00:18:36,764 --> 00:18:39,264
奇跡になる
will become a miracle.

286
00:18:39,264 --> 00:18:44,764
生まれた思いが
