DIVE!

314
00:20:35,539 --> 00:20:38,139
そう 高く
Yes, higher...

315
00:20:38,139 --> 00:20:40,639
果てなく
...and endlessly,

316
00:20:40,639 --> 00:20:43,839
抱きしめた未来が
the future we embraced...

317
00:20:43,839 --> 00:20:46,439
奇跡になる
...will become a miracle.

318
00:20:46,439 --> 00:20:48,939
生まれた
The feelings...

319
00:20:48,939 --> 00:20:51,439
思いが
...that were born...

320
00:20:51,439 --> 00:20:54,639
明日へと 導くよ
